@startuml Abbreviated Workflows
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888

title Dynamic Travel Architect — Abbreviated & Specialized Pipelines

actor "User" as User #LightBlue
participant "Orchestrator" as Orch #LightGoldenRodYellow
participant "PM" as PM #LightGreen
participant "Dev" as Dev #LightSkyBlue
participant "AE" as AE #LightSalmon
participant "Render" as Render #PeachPuff
participant "Regression" as Regr #MistyRose

== Bug Fix Pipeline (PM-Req + Dev-Impl + AE-Exec) ==

User -> Orch : Bug report
activate Orch
Orch -> PM : PM-Req: Write BRD\n(bug description + fix criteria)
activate PM
PM --> Orch : BRD ready
deactivate PM

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Impl: Implement fix\nper BRD
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Fix applied
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Render : Phase 6: Render HTML
activate Render
Render --> Orch : HTML ready
deactivate Render

Orch -> Regr : Phase 6: Run regression
activate Regr
Regr --> Orch : Results
deactivate Regr

Orch --> User : Bug fix validated
deactivate Orch

|||
== Test-Only Update Pipeline (AE-Plan + QA-Review + AE-Impl + AE-Exec) ==

User -> Orch : Test update request
activate Orch
Orch -> AE : AE-Plan: Write/update test_plan.md
activate AE
AE --> Orch : Plan ready
deactivate AE

note over Orch : QA-Review (Phase 4b)\napplies here too

Orch -> AE : AE-Impl: Implement tests
activate AE
AE --> Orch : Tests written
deactivate AE

Orch -> Regr : Phase 6: Run regression
activate Regr
Regr --> Orch : Results
deactivate Regr

Orch --> User : Tests validated
deactivate Orch

|||
== Trip Generation Pipeline (Dev-TripPlanning + Dev-Content — No Dev Cycle) ==

User -> Orch : "Generate trip from trip_details.md"
activate Orch

Orch -> Dev : Dev-TripPlanning: Read trip details,\ncalculate ages, research destination
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Research complete
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Phase A — Write overview.md\n+ manifest.json
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Overview ready
deactivate Dev

note over Orch : No Phase A approval gate\n(auto-proceed to Phase B)

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Phase B — Parallel day generation\n(day_00.md … day_NN.md)
activate Dev
note right of Dev
    Subagents generate
    days in parallel
end note
Dev --> Orch : All days written
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Budget — Aggregate costs\ninto budget.md
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Budget ready
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Assemble — Concat all parts\ninto trip_full.md
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Assembly done
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Render : 6. Generate HTML\n(per-day fragments → trip_full_LANG.html)
activate Render
Render --> Orch : HTML generated
deactivate Render

Orch -> Regr : 7. Validate: Run regression suite
activate Regr
Regr --> Orch : All tests pass
deactivate Regr

Orch --> User : Trip delivered
deactivate Orch

|||
== Incremental Edit Pipeline (Dev-Content + Dev-HTML) ==

User -> Orch : "Change day 3"
activate Orch

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Regenerate day_03.md only
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Day updated
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Dev : Dev-Content: Re-assemble trip_full.md
activate Dev
Dev --> Orch : Reassembled
deactivate Dev

Orch -> Render : Dev-HTML: Incremental HTML rebuild\n(only changed day fragment)
activate Render
Render --> Orch : HTML updated
deactivate Render

Orch -> Regr : AE-Exec: Targeted validation\n(changed day only)
activate Regr
Regr --> Orch : Validated
deactivate Regr

Orch --> User : Edit complete
deactivate Orch

@enduml
